title: Felipe Cybis Pereira
text:
I am currently a PhD candidate studying freely-moving rats with functional Ultrasound imaging 🐀🩻📈.
I work at Physics for Medicine Paris under the supervision of Mickaël Tanter and Sophie Pezet.
